                'description' => "<h3>Overview</h3>\n<p>VIP ATV Safari Program is a premium evening desert experience that combines adventure, culture, and entertainment in the beautiful desert of Sharm El Sheikh. Starting in the afternoon with convenient hotel pickup, this tour takes you deep into the golden dunes for an unforgettable Bedouin night.<br>You will enjoy a full one-hour ATV safari across the desert landscapes, a scenic photo stop at the famous Echo Sound point, and a relaxing stop at a traditional Bedouin tent where you will be served authentic Bedouin tea. As the sun sets, you will arrive at the Bedouin camp for a tasty dinner under the stars. The evening continues with exciting entertainment including dance shows and thrilling fire performances. You will also experience a short 5-minute camel ride, adding to the authentic desert atmosphere. The tour ends with comfortable drop-off back to your hotel.<br>This VIP program is perfect for those seeking a mix of adrenaline, culture, and relaxation in one memorable evening.</p>\n<h3>Trip Highlights</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>One full hour of ATV safari riding through the stunning desert dunes.</li>\n  <li>Scenic photo stops at the unique Echo Sound point in the desert.</li>\n  <li>Traditional Bedouin tea served inside an authentic Bedouin tent.</li>\n  <li>Delicious dinner at the Bedouin camp followed by exciting dance and fire shows.</li>\n  <li>Camel riding experience and convenient hotel pick-up and drop-off service.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Pricing Options</h3>
