                'excluded' => json_encode(['Transfer from ( Makadi ,Sahl hasheesh, Safaga, El-Gouna, Soma Bay ) extra charge 10$ per person']),
                'short_description' => "Experience the highlights of ancient Luxor on a full-day shared tour from Hurghada. Visit the legendary Valley of the Kings, the Temple of Queen Hatshepsut, and the Colossi of Memnon while learning about Egypt’s fascinating history from an expert guide.",
                'description' => "<h3>Overview</h3>\n<p>Join a full-day shared excursion from Hurghada to Luxor and step into the world of ancient Egypt’s pharaohs and monuments. Travel comfortably with fellow travelers and enjoy a guided journey through some of the country’s most remarkable archaeological sites. Begin your adventure at the Valley of the Kings, the renowned royal necropolis where generations of pharaohs were laid to rest. Explore several beautifully decorated tombs and discover the ancient Egyptians’ beliefs about the afterlife through the insights of your experienced guide. Continue to the impressive Temple of Queen Hatshepsut, an architectural masterpiece built in honor of one of Egypt’s most influential rulers. Then visit the Colossi of Memnon, two massive statues that have guarded the ancient Theban necropolis for thousands of years. Throughout the day, your guide will bring Egypt’s rich history to life with captivating stories and expert commentary. With round-trip transportation, lunch, and guided visits included, this shared tour provides a comfortable and enriching way to experience the timeless treasures of Luxor.</p>\n<h3>Trip Highlights</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Explore the legendary Valley of the Kings.</li>\n  <li>Visit the magnificent Temple of Queen Hatshepsut.</li>\n  <li>See the iconic Colossi of Memnon.</li>\n  <li>Learn from a professional Egyptologist guide.</li>\n  <li>Enjoy lunch and comfortable round-trip transportation.</li>\n</ul>",
                'translations' => [
