                'description' => "<h3>Overview</h3>\n<p>Experience an authentic desert adventure from Marsa Alam with this exciting Bedouin Safari. You will be picked up from your hotel in a comfortable 4WD Toyota Land Cruiser. Drive through the breathtaking desert landscape until you reach a traditional Bedouin village. Along the way, your professional guide will stop to explain the famous Akassia tree and desert life. At the village, enjoy warm Bedouin hospitality with welcome tea. Then hop on a quad bike and ride through the scenic desert valleys. You’ll also experience a relaxing camel ride, just like the local Bedouins. After taking beautiful photos, take a guided tour of the village to see traditional bread baking and the old water well. As the sun sets, head to a spectacular viewpoint to enjoy one of the most magnificent desert sunsets. Then return to the cozy Bedouin tent for a delicious open buffet BBQ dinner featuring grilled chicken, kofta, rice, pasta, salads, fresh bread, fruits, and soft drinks. The evening continues with a fun traditional Bedouin party with Egyptian music and dancing. Before heading back to your hotel in Marsa Alam, enjoy the amazing star show in the clear desert sky.</p>\n<h3>Trip Highlights</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Thrilling quad bike ride through the Marsa Alam desert</li>\n  <li>Authentic camel ride at a traditional Bedouin village</li>\n  <li>Breathtaking sunset viewing in the heart of the desert</li>\n  <li>Delicious open buffet BBQ dinner under the stars</li>\n  <li>Vibrant Bedouin party with live music and dancing</li>\n</ul>",
